 646     private void parseHeaderMap (ReadableMap headerMap) {                                                
 647         if (headerMap == null) {                                                                         
 648             return;                                                                                      
 649         }                                                                                                
 650         if (headerMap.hasKey("register") && headerMap.getType("register") == ReadableType.Map) {         
 651             this.registrationRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("register"));
 652         }                                                                                                
 653         if (headerMap.hasKey("authorize") && headerMap.getType("authorize") == ReadableType.Map) {       
 654             this.authorizationRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("authorize")🔵
 655         }                                                                                                
 656         if (headerMap.hasKey("token") && headerMap.getType("token") == ReadableType.Map) {               
 657             this.tokenRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("token"));          
 658         }

 679     /*                                                                                                   
 680      * Create a space-delimited string from an array                                                     
 681      */                                                                                                  
 682     private String arrayToString(ReadableArray array) {                                                  
 683         StringBuilder strBuilder = new StringBuilder();                                                  
 684         for (int i = 0; i < array.size(); i++) {                                                         
 685             if (i != 0) {                                                                                
 686                 strBuilder.append(' ');                                                                  
 687             }                                                                                            
 688             strBuilder.append(array.getString(i));                                                       
 689         }                                                                                                
 690         return strBuilder.toString();                                                                    
 691     }

 697         ArrayList<String> list = new ArrayList<>();                                                      
 698         for (int i = 0; i < array.size(); i++) {                                                         
 699             list.add(array.getString(i));                                                                
 700         }                                                                                                
 701         return list;                                                                                     
 702     }

 756         if (!serviceConfiguration.hasKey("authorizationEndpoint")) {

 759

 768             registrationEndpoint = Uri.parse(serviceConfiguration.getString("registrationEndpoint"));    
 769         }                                                                                                
 770                                                                                                          
 771         return new AuthorizationServiceConfiguration(                                                    
 772                 authorizationEndpoint,                                                                   
 773                 tokenEndpoint,                                                                           
 774                 registrationEndpoint                                                                     
 775         );                                                                                               
 776     }

 801     private void parseHeaderMap (ReadableMap headerMap) {                                                
 802         if (headerMap == null) {                                                                         
 803             return;                                                                                      
 804         }                                                                                                
 805         if (headerMap.hasKey("register") && headerMap.getType("register") == ReadableType.Map) {         
 806             this.registrationRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("register"));
 807         }                                                                                                
 808         if (headerMap.hasKey("authorize") && headerMap.getType("authorize") == ReadableType.Map) {       
 809             this.authorizationRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("authorize")🔵
 810         }                                                                                                
 811         if (headerMap.hasKey("token") && headerMap.getType("token") == ReadableType.Map) {               
 812             this.tokenRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("token"));          
 813         }                                                                                                
 814                                                                                                          
 815     }

 834     /*                                                                                                   
 835      * Create a space-delimited string from an array                                                     
 836      */                                                                                                  
 837     private String arrayToString(ReadableArray array) {                                                  
 838         StringBuilder strBuilder = new StringBuilder();                                                  
 839         for (int i = 0; i < array.size(); i++) {                                                         
 840             if (i != 0) {                                                                                
 841                 strBuilder.append(' ');                                                                  
 842             }                                                                                            
 843             strBuilder.append(array.getString(i));                                                       
 844         }                                                                                                
 845         return strBuilder.toString();                                                                    
 846     }

 855         }

 889             proxiedBuilder = DefaultConnectionBuilder.INSTANCE;                                          
 890         }                                                                                                
 891                                                                                                          
 892         CustomConnectionBuilder customConnection = new CustomConnectionBuilder(proxiedBuilder);          
 893         if (headers != null) {                                                                           
 894             customConnection.setHeaders(headers);                                                        
 895         }                                                                                                
 896                                                                                                          
 897         return customConnection;                                                                         
 898     }

 910     private AuthorizationServiceConfiguration createAuthorizationServiceConfiguration(ReadableMap service🔵
 911         if (!serviceConfiguration.hasKey("authorizationEndpoint")) {                                     
 912             throw new Exception("serviceConfiguration passed without an authorizationEndpoint");         
 913         }                                                                                                
 914                                                                                                          
 915         if (!serviceConfiguration.hasKey("tokenEndpoint")) {                                             
 916             throw new Exception("serviceConfiguration passed without a tokenEndpoint");                  
 917         }                                                                                                
 918                                                                                                          
 919         Uri authorizationEndpoint = Uri.parse(serviceConfiguration.getString("authorizationEndpoint"));  
 920         Uri tokenEndpoint = Uri.parse(serviceConfiguration.getString("tokenEndpoint"));                  
 921         Uri registrationEndpoint = null;                                                                 
 922         if (serviceConfiguration.hasKey("registrationEndpoint")) {                                       
 923             registrationEndpoint = Uri.parse(serviceConfiguration.getString("registrationEndpoint"));    
 924         }                                                                                                
 925                                                                                                          
 926         return new AuthorizationServiceConfiguration(                                                    
 927                 authorizationEndpoint,                                                                   
 928                 tokenEndpoint,                                                                           
 929                 registrationEndpoint                                                                     
 930         );                                                                                               
 931     }

 245     @Override                                                                                            
 246     public void onActivityResult(Activity activity, int requestCode, int resultCode, Intent data) {      
 247         if (requestCode == 0) {                                                                          
 248             if (data == null) {                                                                          
 249                 if (promise != null) {                                                                   
 250                     promise.reject("authentication_error", "Data intent is null");                       
 251                 }                                                                                        
 252                 return;                                                                                  
 253             }                                                                                            
 254             final AuthorizationResponse response = AuthorizationResponse.fromIntent(data);               
 255             AuthorizationException exception = AuthorizationException.fromIntent(data);                  
 256             if (exception != null) {                                                                     
 257                 if (promise != null) {                                                                   
 258                     promise.reject("authentication_error", getErrorMessage(exception));                  
 259                 }                                                                                        
 260                 return;                                                                                  
 261             }                                                                                            
 262             if (this.skipCodeExchange) {                                                                 
 263                 WritableMap map = TokenResponseFactory.authorizationResponseToMap(response);             
 264                 promise.resolve(map);                                                                    
 265                 return;                                                                                  
 266             }                                                                                            
 267             final Promise authorizePromise = this.promise;                                               
 268             final AppAuthConfiguration configuration = createAppAuthConfiguration(createConnectionBuilder🔵
 269             AuthorizationService authService = new AuthorizationService(this.reactContext, configuration)🔵
 270             TokenRequest tokenRequest = response.createTokenExchangeRequest(this.additionalParametersMap)🔵
 271             AuthorizationService.TokenResponseCallback tokenResponseCallback = new AuthorizationService.T🔵
 272                 @Override                                                                                
 273                 public void onTokenRequestCompleted(TokenResponse resp, AuthorizationException ex) {     
 274                     if (resp != null) {                                                                  
 275                         WritableMap map = TokenResponseFactory.tokenResponseToMap(resp, response);       
 276                         if (authorizePromise != null) {                                                  
 277                             authorizePromise.resolve(map);                                               
 278                         }                                                                                
 279                     } else if (promise != null) {                                                        
 280                         promise.reject("token_exchange_failed", getErrorMessage(ex));                    
 281                     }                                                                                    
 282                 }                                                                                        
 283             };                                                                                           
 284             if (this.clientSecret != null) {                                                             
 285                 ClientAuthentication clientAuth = this.getClientAuthentication(this.clientSecret, this.cl🔵
 286                 authService.performTokenRequest(tokenRequest, clientAuth, tokenResponseCallback);        
 287             } else {                                                                                     
 288                 authService.performTokenRequest(tokenRequest, tokenResponseCallback);                    
 289             }                                                                                            
 290         }                                                                                                
 291     }

 315                 )

 317                                                                                                          
 318         if (responseTypes != null) {                                                                     
 319             registrationRequestBuilder.setResponseTypeValues(arrayToList(responseTypes));

 327             registrationRequestBuilder.setSubjectType(subjectType);                                      
 328         }                                                                                                
 329                                                                                                          
 330         if (tokenEndpointAuthMethod != null) {                                                           
 331             registrationRequestBuilder.setTokenEndpointAuthenticationMethod(tokenEndpointAuthMethod);    
 332         }                                                                                                
 333                                                                                                          
 334         RegistrationRequest registrationRequest = registrationRequestBuilder.build();                    
 335

 340                     WritableMap map = RegistrationResponseFactory.registrationResponseToMap(response);   
 341                     promise.resolve(map);                                                                
 342                 } else {                                                                                 
 343                     promise.reject("registration_failed", getErrorMessage(ex));

 347

 349     }

 351     /*                                                                                                   
 352      * Authorize user with the provided configuration                                                    
 353      */                                                                                                  
 354     private void authorizeWithConfiguration(                                                             
 355             final AuthorizationServiceConfiguration serviceConfiguration,                                
 356             final AppAuthConfiguration appAuthConfiguration,                                             
 357             final String clientId,                                                                       
 358             final ReadableArray scopes,                                                                  
 359             final String redirectUrl,                                                                    
 360             final Boolean usePKCE,                                                                       
 361             final Map<String, String> additionalParametersMap                                            
 362     ) {                                                                                                  
 363                                                                                                          
 364         String scopesString = null;                                                                      
 365                                                                                                          
 366         if (scopes != null) {                                                                            
 367             scopesString = this.arrayToString(scopes);                                                   
 368         }                                                                                                
 369                                                                                                          
 370         final Context context = this.reactContext;                                                       
 371         final Activity currentActivity = getCurrentActivity();                                           
 372                                                                                                          
 373         AuthorizationRequest.Builder authRequestBuilder =                                                
 374                 new AuthorizationRequest.Builder(                                                        
 375                         serviceConfiguration,                                                            
 376                         clientId,                                                                        
 377                         ResponseTypeValues.CODE,                                                         
 378                         Uri.parse(redirectUrl)                                                           
 379                 );                                                                                       
 380                                                                                                          
 381         if (scopesString != null) {                                                                      
 382             authRequestBuilder.setScope(scopesString);                                                   
 383         }                                                                                                
 384                                                                                                          
 385                                                                                                          
 386         if (additionalParametersMap != null) {                                                           
 387             // handle additional parameters separately to avoid exceptions from AppAuth                  
 388             if (additionalParametersMap.containsKey("display")) {                                        
 389                 authRequestBuilder.setDisplay(additionalParametersMap.get("display"));                   
 390                 additionalParametersMap.remove("display");                                               
 391             }                                                                                            
 392             if (additionalParametersMap.containsKey("login_hint")) {                                     
 393                 authRequestBuilder.setLoginHint(additionalParametersMap.get("login_hint"));              
 394                 additionalParametersMap.remove("login_hint");                                            
 395             }                                                                                            
 396             if (additionalParametersMap.containsKey("prompt")) {                                         
 397                 authRequestBuilder.setPrompt(additionalParametersMap.get("prompt"));                     
 398                 additionalParametersMap.remove("prompt");                                                
 399             }                                                                                            
 400                                                                                                          
 401             authRequestBuilder.setAdditionalParameters(additionalParametersMap);                         
 402         }                                                                                                
 403                                                                                                          
 404         if (!usePKCE) {                                                                                  
 405             authRequestBuilder.setCodeVerifier(null);                                                    
 406         }                                                                                                
 407                                                                                                          
 408         AuthorizationRequest authRequest = authRequestBuilder.build();                                   
 409                                                                                                          
 410         if (android.os.Build.VERSION.SDK_INT >= android.os.Build.VERSION_CODES.LOLLIPOP) {               
 411             AuthorizationService authService = new AuthorizationService(context, appAuthConfiguration);  
 412             Intent authIntent = authService.getAuthorizationRequestIntent(authRequest);                  
 413                                                                                                          
 414             currentActivity.startActivityForResult(authIntent, 0);                                       
 415         } else {                                                                                         
 416             AuthorizationService authService = new AuthorizationService(currentActivity, appAuthConfigura🔵
 417             PendingIntent pendingIntent = currentActivity.createPendingResult(0, new Intent(), 0);       
 418                                                                                                          
 419             authService.performAuthorizationRequest(authRequest, pendingIntent);                         
 420         }                                                                                                
 421     }

 433             final Map<String, String> additionalParametersMap,

 435             final String clientSecret,                                                                   
 436             final Promise promise                                                                        
 437     ) {                                                                                                  
 438                                                                                                          
 439         String scopesString = null;

 649      private void parseHeaderMap (ReadableMap headerMap) {                                                         
 650          if (headerMap == null) {                                                                                  
 651              return;                                                                                               
 652          }                                                                                                         
 653          if (headerMap.hasKey("register") && headerMap.getType("register") == ReadableType.Map) {                  
 654              this.registrationRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("register"));         
 655          }                                                                                                         
 656          if (headerMap.hasKey("authorize") && headerMap.getType("authorize") == ReadableType.Map) {                
 657              this.authorizationRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("authorize"));       
 658          }                                                                                                         
 659          if (headerMap.hasKey("token") && headerMap.getType("token") == ReadableType.Map) {                        
 660              this.tokenRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("token"));                   
 661          }                                                                                                         
 662                                                                                                                    
 663      }

 682      /*                                                                                                            
 683       * Create a space-delimited string from an array                                                              
 684       */                                                                                                           
 685      private String arrayToString(ReadableArray array) {                                                           
 686          StringBuilder strBuilder = new StringBuilder();                                                           
 687          for (int i = 0; i < array.size(); i++) {                                                                  
 688              if (i != 0) {                                                                                         
 689                  strBuilder.append(' ');                                                                           
 690              }                                                                                                     
 691              strBuilder.append(array.getString(i));                                                                
 692          }                                                                                                         
 693          return strBuilder.toString();                                                                             
 694      }

 375      /*                                                                                                            
 376       * Called when the OAuth browser activity completes                                                           
 377       */                                                                                                           
 378      @Override                                                                                                     
 379      public void onActivityResult(Activity activity, int requestCode, int resultCode, Intent data) {               
 380          if (requestCode == 0) {                                                                                   
 381              if (data == null) {                                                                                   
 382                  if (promise != null) {                                                                            
 383                      promise.reject("authentication_error", "Data intent is null" );                               
 384                  }                                                                                                 
 385                  return;                                                                                           
 386              }                                                                                                     
 387                                                                                                                    
 388              final AuthorizationResponse response = AuthorizationResponse.fromIntent(data);                        
 389              AuthorizationException exception = AuthorizationException.fromIntent(data);                           
 390              if (exception != null) {                                                                              
 391                  if (promise != null) {                                                                            
 392                      promise.reject("authentication_error", getErrorMessage(exception));                           
 393                  }                                                                                                 
 394                  return;                                                                                           
 395              }                                                                                                     
 396                                                                                                                    
 397 +            if (this.skipCodeExchange) {                                                                          
 398 +                WritableMap map = TokenResponseFactory.authorizationResponseToMap(response);                      
 399 +                promise.resolve(map);                                                                             
 400 +                return;                                                                                           
 401 +            }                                                                                                     
 402 +                                                                                                                  
 403 +                                                                                                                  
 404              final Promise authorizePromise = this.promise;                                                        
 405              final AppAuthConfiguration configuration = createAppAuthConfiguration(                                
 406                      createConnectionBuilder(this.dangerouslyAllowInsecureHttpRequests, this.tokenRequestHeaders)  
 407              );                                                                                                    
 408                                                                                                                    
 409              AuthorizationService authService = new AuthorizationService(this.reactContext, configuration);        
 410                                                                                                                    
 411              TokenRequest tokenRequest = response.createTokenExchangeRequest(this.additionalParametersMap);        
 412                                                                                                                    
 413              AuthorizationService.TokenResponseCallback tokenResponseCallback = new AuthorizationService.TokenRespo🔵
 414                                                                                                                    
 415                  @Override                                                                                         
 416                  public void onTokenRequestCompleted(                                                              
 417                          TokenResponse resp, AuthorizationException ex) {                                          
 418                      if (resp != null) {                                                                           
 419                          WritableMap map = TokenResponseFactory.tokenResponseToMap(resp, response);                
 420                          if (authorizePromise != null) {                                                           
 421                              authorizePromise.resolve(map);                                                        
 422                          }                                                                                         
 423                      } else {                                                                                      
 424                          if (promise != null) {                                                                    
 425                              promise.reject("token_exchange_failed", getErrorMessage(ex));                         
 426                          }                                                                                         
 427                      }                                                                                             
 428                  }                                                                                                 
 429              };                                                                                                    
 430                                                                                                                    
 431              if (this.clientSecret != null) {                                                                      
 432                  ClientAuthentication clientAuth = this.getClientAuthentication(this.clientSecret, this.clientAuthM🔵
 433                  authService.performTokenRequest(tokenRequest, clientAuth, tokenResponseCallback);                 
 434                                                                                                                    
 435              } else {                                                                                              
 436                  authService.performTokenRequest(tokenRequest, tokenResponseCallback);                             
 437              }                                                                                                     
 438                                                                                                                    
 439          }                                                                                                         
 440      }

 500      /*                                                                                                            
 501       * Authorize user with the provided configuration                                                             
 502       */                                                                                                           
 503      private void authorizeWithConfiguration(                                                                      
 504              final AuthorizationServiceConfiguration serviceConfiguration,                                         
 505              final AppAuthConfiguration appAuthConfiguration,                                                      
 506              final String clientId,                                                                                
 507              final ReadableArray scopes,                                                                           
 508              final String redirectUrl,                                                                             
 509              final Boolean usePKCE,                                                                                
 510              final Map<String, String> additionalParametersMap                                                     
 511      ) {                                                                                                           
 512                                                                                                                    
 513          String scopesString = null;                                                                               
 514                                                                                                                    
 515          if (scopes != null) {                                                                                     
 516              scopesString = this.arrayToString(scopes);                                                            
 517          }                                                                                                         
 518                                                                                                                    
 519          final Context context = this.reactContext;                                                                
 520          final Activity currentActivity = getCurrentActivity();                                                    
 521                                                                                                                    
 522          AuthorizationRequest.Builder authRequestBuilder =                                                         
 523                  new AuthorizationRequest.Builder(                                                                 
 524                          serviceConfiguration,                                                                     
 525                          clientId,                                                                                 
 526                          ResponseTypeValues.CODE,                                                                  
 527                          Uri.parse(redirectUrl)                                                                    
 528                  );                                                                                                
 529                                                                                                                    
 530          if (scopesString != null) {                                                                               
 531              authRequestBuilder.setScope(scopesString);                                                            
 532          }                                                                                                         
 533                                                                                                                    
 534                                                                                                                    
 535          if (additionalParametersMap != null) {                                                                    
 536              // handle additional parameters separately to avoid exceptions from AppAuth                           
 537              if (additionalParametersMap.containsKey("display")) {                                                 
 538                  authRequestBuilder.setDisplay(additionalParametersMap.get("display"));                            
 539                  additionalParametersMap.remove("display");                                                        
 540              }                                                                                                     
 541              if (additionalParametersMap.containsKey("login_hint")) {                                              
 542                  authRequestBuilder.setLoginHint(additionalParametersMap.get("login_hint"));                       
 543                  additionalParametersMap.remove("login_hint");                                                     
 544              }                                                                                                     
 545              if (additionalParametersMap.containsKey("prompt")) {                                                  
 546                  authRequestBuilder.setPrompt(additionalParametersMap.get("prompt"));                              
 547                  additionalParametersMap.remove("prompt");                                                         
 548              }                                                                                                     
 549                                                                                                                    
 550              authRequestBuilder.setAdditionalParameters(additionalParametersMap);                                  
 551          }                                                                                                         
 552                                                                                                                    
 553          if (!usePKCE) {                                                                                           
 554              authRequestBuilder.setCodeVerifier(null);                                                             
 555          }                                                                                                         
 556                                                                                                                    
 557          AuthorizationRequest authRequest = authRequestBuilder.build();                                            
 558                                                                                                                    
 559          if (android.os.Build.VERSION.SDK_INT >= android.os.Build.VERSION_CODES.LOLLIPOP) {                        
 560              AuthorizationService authService = new AuthorizationService(context, appAuthConfiguration);           
 561              Intent authIntent = authService.getAuthorizationRequestIntent(authRequest);                           
 562                                                                                                                    
 563              currentActivity.startActivityForResult(authIntent, 0);                                                
 564          } else {                                                                                                  
 565              AuthorizationService authService = new AuthorizationService(currentActivity, appAuthConfiguration);   
 566              PendingIntent pendingIntent = currentActivity.createPendingResult(0, new Intent(), 0);                
 567                                                                                                                    
 568              authService.performAuthorizationRequest(authRequest, pendingIntent);                                  
 569          }                                                                                                         
 570      }

 572      /*                                                                                                            
 573       * Refresh authentication token with the provided configuration                                               
 574       */                                                                                                           
 575      private void refreshWithConfiguration(                                                                        
 576              final AuthorizationServiceConfiguration serviceConfiguration,                                         
 577              final AppAuthConfiguration appAuthConfiguration,                                                      
 578              final String refreshToken,                                                                            
 579              final String clientId,                                                                                
 580              final ReadableArray scopes,                                                                           
 581              final String redirectUrl,                                                                             
 582              final Map<String, String> additionalParametersMap,                                                    
 583              final String clientAuthMethod,                                                                        
 584              final String clientSecret,                                                                            
 585              final Promise promise                                                                                 
 586      ) {                                                                                                           
 587                                                                                                                    
 588          String scopesString = null;                                                                               
 589                                                                                                                    
 590          if (scopes != null) {                                                                                     
 591              scopesString = this.arrayToString(scopes);                                                            
 592          }                                                                                                         
 593                                                                                                                    
 594          final Context context = this.reactContext;                                                                
 595                                                                                                                    
 596          TokenRequest.Builder tokenRequestBuilder =                                                                
 597                  new TokenRequest.Builder(                                                                         
 598                          serviceConfiguration,                                                                     
 599                          clientId                                                                                  
 600                  )                                                                                                 
 601                          .setRefreshToken(refreshToken)                                                            
 602                          .setRedirectUri(Uri.parse(redirectUrl));                                                  
 603                                                                                                                    
 604          if (scopesString != null) {                                                                               
 605              tokenRequestBuilder.setScope(scopesString);                                                           
 606          }                                                                                                         
 607                                                                                                                    
 608          if (!additionalParametersMap.isEmpty()) {                                                                 
 609              tokenRequestBuilder.setAdditionalParameters(additionalParametersMap);                                 
 610          }                                                                                                         
 611                                                                                                                    
 612          TokenRequest tokenRequest = tokenRequestBuilder.build();                                                  
 613                                                                                                                    
 614          AuthorizationService authService = new AuthorizationService(context, appAuthConfiguration);               
 615                                                                                                                    
 616          AuthorizationService.TokenResponseCallback tokenResponseCallback = new AuthorizationService.TokenResponseC🔵
 617              @Override                                                                                             
 618              public void onTokenRequestCompleted(@Nullable TokenResponse response, @Nullable AuthorizationException🔵
 619                  if (response != null) {                                                                           
 620                      WritableMap map = TokenResponseFactory.tokenResponseToMap(response);                          
 621                      promise.resolve(map);                                                                         
 622                  } else {                                                                                          
 623                      promise.reject("token_refresh_failed", getErrorMessage(ex));                                  
 624                  }                                                                                                 
 625              }                                                                                                     
 626          };                                                                                                        
 627                                                                                                                    
 628                                                                                                                    
 629          if (clientSecret != null) {                                                                               
 630              ClientAuthentication clientAuth = this.getClientAuthentication(clientSecret, clientAuthMethod);       
 631              authService.performTokenRequest(tokenRequest, clientAuth, tokenResponseCallback);                     
 632                                                                                                                    
 633          } else {                                                                                                  
 634              authService.performTokenRequest(tokenRequest, tokenResponseCallback);                                 
 635          }                                                                                                         
 636      }

 638      private void parseHeaderMap (ReadableMap headerMap) {                                                         
 639          if (headerMap == null) {                                                                                  
 640              return;                                                                                               
 641          }                                                                                                         
 642          if (headerMap.hasKey("register") && headerMap.getType("register") == ReadableType.Map) {                  
 643              this.registrationRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("register"));         
 644          }                                                                                                         
 645          if (headerMap.hasKey("authorize") && headerMap.getType("authorize") == ReadableType.Map) {                
 646              this.authorizationRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("authorize"));       
 647          }                                                                                                         
 648          if (headerMap.hasKey("token") && headerMap.getType("token") == ReadableType.Map) {                        
 649              this.tokenRequestHeaders = MapUtil.readableMapToHashMap(headerMap.getMap("token"));                   
 650          }                                                                                                         
 651                                                                                                                    
 652      }

 654      private ClientAuthentication getClientAuthentication(String clientSecret, String clientAuthMethod) {          
 655          if (clientAuthMethod.equals("post")) {                                                                    
 656              return new ClientSecretPost(clientSecret);                                                            
 657          }                                                                                                         
 658                                                                                                                    
 659          return new ClientSecretBasic(clientSecret);                                                               
 660      }

 662      /*                                                                                                            
 663       * Return error information if it is available                                                                
 664       */                                                                                                           
 665      private String getErrorMessage(AuthorizationException ex){                                                    
 666          if(ex.errorDescription == null && ex.error != null)                                                       
 667              return ex.error;                                                                                      
 668          return ex.errorDescription;                                                                               
 669      }

 671      /*                                                                                                            
 672       * Create a space-delimited string from an array                                                              
 673       */                                                                                                           
 674      private String arrayToString(ReadableArray array) {                                                           
 675          StringBuilder strBuilder = new StringBuilder();                                                           
 676          for (int i = 0; i < array.size(); i++) {                                                                  
 677              if (i != 0) {                                                                                         
 678                  strBuilder.append(' ');                                                                           
 679              }                                                                                                     
 680              strBuilder.append(array.getString(i));                                                                
 681          }                                                                                                         
 682          return strBuilder.toString();                                                                             
 683      }

 686       * Create a string list from an array of strings                                                              
 687       */                                                                                                           
 688      private List<String> arrayToList(ReadableArray array) {                                                       
 689          ArrayList<String> list = new ArrayList<>();                                                               
 690          for (int i = 0; i < array.size(); i++) {                                                                  
 691              list.add(array.getString(i));                                                                         
 692          }                                                                                                         
 693          return list;                                                                                              
 694      }

 699      private List<Uri> arrayToUriList(ReadableArray array) {

 747      private AuthorizationServiceConfiguration createAuthorizationServiceConfiguration(ReadableMap serviceConfigura🔵
 748          if (!serviceConfiguration.hasKey("authorizationEndpoint")) {                                              
 749              throw new Exception("serviceConfiguration passed without an authorizationEndpoint");                  
 750          }                                                                                                         
 751                                                                                                                    
 752          if (!serviceConfiguration.hasKey("tokenEndpoint")) {                                                      
 753              throw new Exception("serviceConfiguration passed without a tokenEndpoint");                           
 754          }                                                                                                         
 755                                                                                                                    
 756          Uri authorizationEndpoint = Uri.parse(serviceConfiguration.getString("authorizationEndpoint"));           
 757          Uri tokenEndpoint = Uri.parse(serviceConfiguration.getString("tokenEndpoint"));                           
 758          Uri registrationEndpoint = null;                                                                          
 759          if (serviceConfiguration.hasKey("registrationEndpoint")) {                                                
 760              registrationEndpoint = Uri.parse(serviceConfiguration.getString("registrationEndpoint"));             
 761          }                                                                                                         
 762                                                                                                                    
 763          return new AuthorizationServiceConfiguration(                                                             
 764                  authorizationEndpoint,                                                                            
 765                  tokenEndpoint,                                                                                    
 766                  registrationEndpoint                                                                              
 767          );                                                                                                        
 768      }
